宣言。”</p><p>今年早些时候，哈尔西<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-shares-health-update-on-endometriosis-3595530#:~:text=Halsey%20has%20shared%20a%20health%20update%20on%20her%20endometriosis%20battle.&amp;text=The%20'Ghost'%20singer%20took%20to,stomach%2C%20covered%20in%20several%20bandages.">还向粉丝们通报了她在与子宫内膜异位症斗争后的健康状况</a>。 “又穿上尿布了，但至少有小蝴蝶结，”她在照片旁边写道，似乎是在接受手术后。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/for-my-last-trick-halsey-seems-to-be-teasing-a-new-era-3761265">“我的最后一招”——哈尔西似乎在戏弄一个新时代，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
